abstract: >-
  Public schema, prompt pack, baseline scoring engine, and interoperability artefacts for the Agenticracy Metric: a public standard for measuring narrative-substrate congruence, observer validation, noise/slop, state classes, action classes, and cost-quality telemetry in AI-generated outputs.
